Jorge Ramos: Amnesty For Illegals, Migrants - 'Nothing We Can Do To Stop Them'
Response:
Here's what's happening Jorge !!
What is the incentive for becoming a citizen?
You have two families: "Citizen Joe" and "Illegal Alien George". Both families have two parents, two children, and live in just about any Major US city !. Joe works in construction, has a Social Security Number and makes $25.00 per hour with taxes deducted.
Illegal Alien George also works in construction, has NO Social Security Number, and gets paid $15.00 cash "under the table."
Ready?
Now pay attention....
Citizen Joe: $25.00 per hour x 40 hours = $1000.00 per week, or $52,000.00 per year. Now take 30% away for state and federal tax. Joe now has $31,231.00.
Illegal Alien George: $15.00 per hour x 40 hours = $600.00 per week, or $31,200.00 per year. George pays no taxes. George now has $31,200.00.
Citizen Joe pays medical and dental insurance with limited coverage for his family at $600.00 per month, or $7,200.00 per year. Joe now has $24,031.00.
Illegal Alien George has full medical and dental coverage through the state and local clinics at a cost of $0.00 per year. George still has $31,200.00.
Citizen Joe makes too much money and is not eligible for food stamps or welfare. Joe pays $500.00 per month for food, or $6,000.00 per year. Joe now has $18,031.00.
Illegal Alien George has no documented income and is eligible for food stamps, welfare, and other social programs. George still has $31,200.00.
Citizen Joe pays rent of $1,200.00 per month, or $14,400.00 per year. Joe now has $9,631.00.
Illegal Alien George receives a $500.00 per month federal rent subsidy,...which pays 80% of his rent George pays out that $500.00 per month, ....or $6,000.00 per year George still has $ 31,200.00.
Citizen Joe pays $200.00 per month, or $2,400.00 for auto insurance. Joe now has $7,231.00.
Illegal Alien George says, "We don't need no stinkin' insurance!" and still has $31,200.00.
Citizen Joe now works overtime on Saturdays or gets a part-time job after work.
Illegal Alien George has nights and weekends off to enjoy with his family.
Citizen Joe and Illegal Alien George’s children both attend the same school. Joe pays for his children's lunches, while George’s children get a government sponsored lunch.
Citizen Joe has to make his $7,231.00 stretch to pay utilities, gas, living expenses. Illegal Alien George has $31,200.00 to pay utilities, gas, and what he sends out of the country every month.
Citizen Joe, works hard, does the right thing, and is barely able to live above the poverty level. Illegal Alien George with his free government entitlements makes $65,000.00 a year CASH and lives tax free!
Illegal Alien George has NO Incentive...to become a legal citizen!
Wake the fuk up America!
70+% of Americans can't name the 3 branches of government or the components of the 1st Amendment.
